
# Dataset : mtcars

    Q : How can one calculate the average miles per gallon (mpg) by number of cylinders in the car (cyl)?

       library(datasets)
       data(mtcars)
       ?mtcars
       sapplz(split(mtcars$mpg, mtcars$cyl), mean)
    
    Answer : 
	       4        6        8 
        26.66364 19.74286 15.10000 


    Q : What R code returns a vector of the means of the variables 'Sepal.Length', 'Sepal.Width', 'Petal.Length', and 'Petal.Width'?
         
    Answer : apply(iris[, 1:4], 2, mean)


       


   
